{"tid":1184849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 距香港220公里】陽江核電站系統調節閥異常 港保安局接獲通報","createTime":"2019-06-04T01:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T03:59:24.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"489b69059b18e69498c54483d3ac0653ef14aae3","tid":1184849,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190603/large/1559565850_f811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190603%2Flarge%2F1559565850_f811.jpg&h=9227012b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陽江核電站距離香港僅220公里。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n距離香港220公里、位於廣東省陽江市東平鎮的陽江核電站通報，該核電站的5號機組，日前在停機檢查時，發生異常事故。在試驗時，汽輪機旁路系統調節閥控制模式出現異常，工作人員及時將模式恢復至正常狀態。核電站根據國際原子能機構的國際核和放射事件分級表，將事件評定爲0級事件，意即未有造成公眾及環境污染。<br />\n<br />\n香港保安局接到陽江核電公司通報事件，並指目前核電站所有正在運作的機組，都保持安全穩定運行。<br />\n<br />\n陽江核電站在2008年動工，1號機組在2014年3月25日投產，而發生事故的5號機組，則是在2013年9月動工，去年5月23日開始運行。該廠第1期的4個機組，均採用由中國改良的壓水式反應堆發電，而第2期的5號及正在興建的6號機組，則用改進型號ACPR-1000反應堆發電，同時為內地首個使用同類反應堆的核電站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190603/59673329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59673329&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eokxx3ZeYPbPBc9Z3MXbd07rU%3D&h=01c2e4a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59673329&h=773e42a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190603/59673329</a>"},{"pid":"7418eff8aa1bff4f608a780aabb7a0383748dc23","tid":1184849,"uid":73804,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T02:13:27.000Z","msg":"又異常事故 又正常運作即係點<br />\n當我地傻？"},{"pid":"534df48981595f95a64551dbbbf30de82c0bdc38","tid":1184849,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"香港廣東統一獨立 先可以確保安全"},{"pid":"fd63ac0ea0174ac30da4765b05ca26e044d6b659","tid":1184849,"uid":218106,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"佢公報得一定係小事<br />\n<br />\n至於大事就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ea75369e9206fa3a9ea394ade2a0a649f7588e","tid":1184849,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T02:52:28.000Z","msg":"大灣區核爆機遇初現曙光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08816988cc0d03af1174ce61d6e2289d5a3649e5","tid":1184849,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"香港其實好易係任何情況下攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73f532990edd8e37ef839226ae41dd236cb19c9","tid":1184849,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"呢期睇緊 HBO 套 Chernobyl, 大陸明顯係放定個炸彈喺香港, 一有咩事就扮核事故"}]}